file.name: openapi_simple_example.yaml
file.content:
---
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Simple OpenAPI
paths:
  "/pets":
    get:
      operationId: listPets
      responses:
        '200':
          description: an array of pets
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  type: object
                  required:
                    - id
                    - name
                  properties:
                    id:
                      type: integer
                      format: int64
                    name:
                      type: string
                    tag:
                      type: string
